title: Black Swan and the Horror of Perfectionism
itunes:title: Black Swan and the Horror of Perfectionism
description:
What's the cost of being perfect? Of losing yourself in the name of performance? Why do we applaud women's pain? The film Black Swan sets the stage for a conversation around the line between art and life, toxic mother-daughter relationships, mental health, symbolism, doppelgangers, ageism, orgasms, and the dangers of perfectionism. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
